    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a prime example of mid-engine engineering, powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six producing linear power through the rev range. The M97 power plant features VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain delivers a visceral connection to the pavement. The chassis is equipped with a sport-tuned McPherson strut arrangement and four-piston monobloc calipers, ensuring neutral handling and consistent thermal management during spirited driving. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and updated shift cables to ensure tactile gear selection. While the exterior shows minor road-wear typical of an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and compression\u2014remain robust and within factory tolerances.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
