    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking luxury without the new-car price tag. The exterior is finished in a timeless Eminent White Pearl; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia from highway driving, the paint retains a deep, glossy luster. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring Parchment leather upholstery that has been kept clean and conditioned, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the premium navigation system and multi-zone climate control, function perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine remains smooth and responsive, backed by a complete service history performed at scheduled intervals. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a new set of all-season tires. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks, offering a quiet and composed ride for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
